anda|title=Chad Michael Murray & More Join Bruce Willis In \u2018The Long Night\u2019|date=14 June 2019|publisher=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/chad-michael-murray-shea-buckner-bruce-willis-the-long-night-1202632807/|accessdate=29 February 2020}}</ref> is an upcoming American action thriller film directed by [[Matt Eskandari]], starring [[Chad Michael Murray]] and [[Bruce Willis]].\n\n==Cast==\n*[[Bruce Willis]] as Frank\n*[[Chad Michael Murray]] as Rich\n*[[Shea Buckner]] as Jamie\n*Tyler Jon Olson as Matthias\n*Lydia Hull as Jan\n*Jessica Abrams as Rachel\n\n==Production==\nPrincipal photography took place in [[Columbus, Georgia]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Kiesewetter|first=John|title=Bruce Willis Shooting Fourth Movie In Cincinnati|date=30 January 2020|publisher=[[WVXU]]|url=https://www.wvxu.org/post/bruce-willis-shooting-fourth-movie-cincinnati#stream/0|accessdate=29 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rice|first=Mark|title=What was it like to be on the Bruce Willis movie set? We asked locals who were there.|date=26 August 2019|publisher=[[Ledger-Enquirer]]|url=https://www.ledger-enquirer.com/entertainment/article234168452.html|accessdate=29 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=smith|first=Tandra|title=Columbus-filmed movie starring Bruce Willis now has a trailer. Watch it here.|date=24 March 2020|publisher=[[Ledger-Enquirer]]|url=https://www.ledger-enquirer.com/entertainment/article241468966.html|accessdate=1 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb title|10303324}}\n*{{rotten-tomatoes|survive_the_night_2020}}\n\n[[Category:Upcoming films]]\n[[Category:American films]]\n[[Category:American action thriller films]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Georgia (U.S. state)]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2020 film}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Survive the Night\n| image          = Survive the Night poster.jpg\n| caption        = \n| director       = [[Matt Eskandari]]\n| producers      = [